mcp-sdk (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of MCP SDK
  * Provides client and server libraries for Model Context Protocol
  * Includes HTTP, HTTPS, and IPC transport support
  * Comprehensive logging and error handling
  * Cross-platform compatibility
  * Example programs and tools included

